Superbrands EA hosted a tribute ceremony on Friday evening at the Villa Rosa Kempinski, Nairobi, to acknowledge 53 top brands in the region.The evening started with a champagne reception at 6.30pm before the awards ceremony at 7.15pm. First Lady Margaret Kenyatta was the chief guest and was also honoured for her Beyond Zero Initiative.Also in attendance were Kenya Red Cross Society secretary general Abbas Gullet, RMA Kenya chief executive Sanjiv Shah and Media Owners Association chairman Dr Hannington Gaya.